quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  3,1,"Alif, Lam, Mim"
  3,2,"Allah There is no god but He, the Living, the Sustainer"
  3,3,He hath revealed unto thee the Book with truth confirming that which went before it; and He sent down the Taurat and Injil
  3,4,"Aforetime, for a guidance unto the people, and sent down the criterion. Verily those who disbelieve in the signs of Allah Unto them shall be torment severe. And Allah is Mighty, Lord of Retribution"
  3,5,Verily Allah aught is concealed from Him in the earth or in the
  3,6,"He it is Who fashionoth You in the Wombs as He will: there is no god but He, the Mighty, the Wise"
  3,7,"He it is who hath sent down unto thee the Book, wherein some verses are firmly constructed they are the mother of the Book: and others consimilar. But those in whose hearts is and deviation follow that which is consimilar therein, seeking discord and seeking to misinterpret the same whereas none knoweth the interpretation thereof a save Allah. And the firmly- grounded in knowledge Say: we believe therein, the whole is from our Lord. And none receiveth admonition save men of understanding"
  3,8,"Our Lord Suffer not our hearts to deviate after that Thou hast guided US, and bestow from Thine presence mercy. Verily Thou! Thou art the Bestower"
  3,9,Our Lord! verily Thou art the Assembler of mankind for a Day whereof there is no doubt. Verily Allah faileth not the tryst